cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CE, cs.DS, cs.SE 

Reasoning systems and decision-making are the main topics of this paper, which are closely related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the use of heuristics and approximation procedures, which are common in computational engineering (cs.CE) and data structures (cs.DS). Additionally, the paper addresses the application of decision theory to control the solution of difficult problems, which is relevant to software engineering (cs.SE).
